<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Automatic Clock-Out Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF7A29 0%, #FF5757 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      opacity: 0.95;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .alert-box {
      background: #FFF3CD;
      border: 2px solid #FF7A29;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .alert-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #FF5757;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .alert-box p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      color: #666;
    }
    .info-card {
      background: #FFF5ED;
      border: 2px solid #FF8C42;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #FFE0CC;
    }
    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
    }
    .info-value {
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #FF5757;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF7A29 0%, #FF5757 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .notice {
      background: #E7F3FF;
      border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .notice p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #1976D2;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      body { padding: 10px; }
      .header { padding: 20px; }
      .header h1 { font-size: 22px; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .info-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>⏰ Automatic Clock-Out</h1>
    <p>{{companyName}}</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <div class="alert-box">
      <h3>🔔 You've Been Automatically Clocked Out</h3>
      <p>You've been working for <span class="highlight">{{hoursWorked}} hours</span> and have reached the maximum work limit of 5 hours per session.</p>
      <p>For your safety and well-being, our system has automatically clocked you out.</p>
    </div>
    
    <h3 style="color: #333; margin: 30px 0 15px 0;">📊 Work Session Details</h3>
    
    <div class="info-card">
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Clock-In Time:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{clockInTime}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Auto Clock-Out Time:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{clockOutTime}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Total Hours Worked:</span>
        <span class="info-value highlight">{{hoursWorked}} hours</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="notice">
      <p><strong>💡 What This Means:</strong></p>
      <p>• Your time log has been saved with all breaks included</p>
      <p>• You can clock in again when you're ready to start a new shift</p>
      <p>• This automatic clock-out ensures compliance with labor regulations</p>
    </div>
    
    <h3 style="color: #333; margin: 30px 0 15px 0;">⚡ Next Steps</h3>
    
    <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Please ensure you take adequate rest before your next shift</li>
      <li>If you believe this was an error, contact your supervisor or HR</li>
      <li>Review your time log in the system to verify accuracy</li>
      <li>Clock in again when you return for your next shift</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/employee/punch-logs" class="button">View My Time Logs</a>
    </div>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px; background: #FFF5ED; border-radius: 8px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>Why 5 Hours?</strong> This limit is in place to protect employee health and safety,
        ensure compliance with labor laws, and maintain work-life balance. If you have questions 
        about this policy, please speak with your manager.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated notification from BizBuddy.</p>
    <p>© {{currentYear}} BizBuddy LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #999;">
      If you have any concerns about this automatic clock-out, please contact your supervisor.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
